name: Absorb
description: These layers of experiencing reality whether subtle or gross, whether seemingly concentrated or airy seem to be all a Dream.. an extremely limited form of perception based on our responses to memories. We create this world which we absorb like a sponge all infused with infinite stories which seem so separate from each other yet these seemingly separate forms in its true essence are so intricately intertwined and playing out with such beauty and intelligence. Music created using generative processing and explorations. Have always loved exploring soundscapes and this comes as a beautiful way of sharing alongside my visual Journey.
